  "title" : "unchecked input for loop condition",
  "body" : "<p>I am getting unchecked input for loop condition at below lines in my code.</p>\n<pre><code>String FirstName= request.getParameter(&quot;FirstName&quot;) !=null ?request.getParameter(&quot;FirstName&quot;):&quot;&quot;;\n</code></pre>\n<p>I have provided below solutions but checkmarx scan still showing same error.</p>\n<pre><code>if(!FirstName.equals(&quot;&quot;)){\nFirstName=ESAPI.validator().getValidInput(&quot;requestParameter&quot;,FirstName,&quot;HTTPParameterValue&quot;, 2000, true);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>I have used getValidinteger() method also but both didn't seems to resolve the issue.</p>\n<p>Here is for loop--</p>\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;String&gt; userDetails = UserData.getDetails(FirstName);\n\nfor(int i=0;i&lt;=userDetails.size();i++){\n   String rollno=userDetails.get(0)!=null?userDetails.get(0):&quot;&quot;;\n   String subject=userDetails.get(1)!=null?userDetails.get(1):&quot;&quot;;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
